# Axtreo Engineering Rules

Stack: React 19 + TypeScript + Vite + Tailwind CSS 4 | Cloudflare Worker + Hono (prod) | Express + tsx (dev) | PostgreSQL 16 + Prisma v7.5.0 | Custom auth (magic link + OTP + TOTP + Google GIS) | Gmail API | Gemini 2.0 Flash | Cloudflare Pages

Never suggest: Firebase Auth, Resend, SES, Render, Vercel, Fastify, SQLite (prod), MongoDB.

## Golden Rule
accountId = security boundary. From session middleware ONLY. Never from req.body or query params.

## Security
- No API keys in client code. Server env vars only.
- Validate all input server-side (shape + type + length).
- CORS: named origins only, never * in production.
- CSP scriptSrc must include apis.google.com + accounts.google.com (dev AND prod).
- Post-login redirects: validate with /^\/[^/]/ regex.

## Design
Background #FAF8F3, Surface #FFFEFB, Accent #E85820, Text #1C1210.
Use Tailwind stone-* only. Never zinc-* or slate-* on light sections.
text-background-dark on cream = invisible. Use text-[#1C1210] on light, text-white on dark.

## Data
Soft deletes via deletedAt on all financial models. No hard deletes.
AuditEvent = append-only. Never delete.
fiscal_month computed on write. Never re-derived at read.
Dashboard reads from ReconciliationRun / RevenueBridgeRun, never raw CashLedgerFact.
Money fields: Decimal type (never Float). Multi-step writes: $transaction().

## Workflow
branch → PR → merge. Never push directly to main.
Review format: 🔴 Critical | 🟡 Suggestion | 🟢 Praise

## Style
Terse. Drop articles, filler, pleasantries. Fragments OK. [thing] [action] [reason]. [next step].
Exception: security warnings + destructive ops = full sentences.
Output: quick=1-4 sentences | bug=diff+1 line | feature=full impl | design=rec+tradeoff+next
